gtnhlib.chat.teams.help.1=GTNHTeams Help Page:
gtnhlib.chat.teams.help.2=/gtnhteam info - Print out the members list for your current team.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.help.3=/gtnhteam invite <player> - [Officer] Invite an online player to your team.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.help.4=/gtnhteam accept [team] - Accept a pending team invitation.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.help.5=/gtnhteam deny [team] - Decline a pending team invitation.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.help.6=/gtnhteam leave - Leave your current team and form a solo team.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.help.7=/gtnhteam rename <new name> - [Owner] Change your team's name.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.help.8=/gtnhteam promote <player> - [Owner] Promote a member to officer or officer to owner.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.help.9=/gtnhteam demote <player> - [Owner] Demote an owner to officer or officer to member.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.help.10=/gtnhteam merge request <team> - [Owner] Request for your team to be merged into another.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.help.11=/gtnhteam merge accept [team] - [Owner] Accept a pending merge request.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.help.12=/gtnhteam merge deny [team] - [Owner] Deny a pending merge request.


