gtnhlib.chat.teams.admin.help.1=GTNHTeams Admin Help Page:
gtnhlib.chat.teams.admin.help.2=/gtnhteam_admin info <team> - Print members list for targeted team.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.admin.help.3=/gtnhteam_admin rename <team> <new name> - Forcibly rename targeted team.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.admin.help.4=/gtnhteam_admin promote <team> <player> - Forcibly promote targeted player in team.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.admin.help.5=/gtnhteam_admin demote <team> <player> - Forcibly demote targeted player in team.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.admin.help.6=/gtnhteam_admin merge <source team> <target team> - Forcibly merge source team into target team, transferring their members and merging data.
gtnhlib.chat.teams.admin.help.7=/gtnhteam_admin disband <team> - Forcibly disband team. Players will be immediately placed into solo teams and the team's data will be permanently lost.

